: reset-board
    0 #checker !
    7 0 do 7 0 do 0 i j place c! loop loop
    7 0 do 1 i 1 place! 1 black i 6 place! loop
    3 0 do
	i 2 + i 0 place!
	i 2 black + i 7 place!
	i 2 black + 7 i - 7 place!
	i 2 + dup 5 = if drop 6 then 7 i - 0 place!
	i 2 + dup 5 = if drop 6 then black  7 i - 7 place!
    loop
;






